comments: Brown (BOS) advances the ball over the mid-court line within 8 seconds.
Siakam (TOR) and Williams (BOS) engage and disengage and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Siakam (TOR) maintains his right hand on the side of the ball during his dribble.
Horford (BOS) initiates contact with Siakam's (TOR) right arm, which affects his SQBR during the drive.
Brogdon (BOS) maintains his left pivot foot while he briefly loses his balance at the start of his dribble.
Pritchard (BOS) is already losing control of the ball prior to the marginal arm contact from Trent Jr. (TOR) on the perimeter.
Siakam (TOR) rests a forearm on Williams' (BOS) back before releasing away and marginal contact occurs as the rebound sails overhead.
Williams (BOS) and Siakam (TOR) engage in marginal arm to arm contact during the rebound.
Williams (BOS) is sliding toward Trent Jr.'s (TOR) path and Trent Jr. moves through marginal body contact during the drive.
During the drive, Trent Jr.'s (TOR) right arm makes incidental contact with Williams'(BOS) midsection.
Williams (BOS) applies a slight forearm on Trent Jr.'s (TOR) side before removing it and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Achiuwa (TOR) swipes down and makes contact with Pritchard's (BOS) left arm, which affects his pass attempt.
Horford (BOS) makes incidental hand-on-ball contact with Siakam (TOR) when the ball is dislodged during his driving shot attempt.
TOR and BOS are incorrectly whistled for a jump ball.
The game is stopped to re-jump the jump ball.
A jump ball is correctly whistled as Barnes (TOR) and Horford (BOS) tie the ball up.

Williams (BOS) uses two hands to dislodge Trent Jr. (TOR) from his legally obtained guarding position. Following the foul, the ball should have been inbounded from where it was at the point of interruption (the 28' mark), rather than from the free throw line extended.
Brown (BOS) is sliding toward Siakam's (TOR) path and marginal body contact occurs as Siakam loses control of the ball.
